messages.subject: Waterpark Gathering
messages.msgSnippet: I just registered for the Winter Waterpark Gathering in Ohio in February. We re really excited about going! I just wanted to remind folks that the Early Bird
messages.messageBody:
I just registered for the Winter Waterpark Gathering in Ohio in February. We're really excited about going!



I just wanted to remind folks that the Early Bird deadline is October 31. You may certainly register and get a room *after* that, but the best deal can be had before November.




Halloween is fast approaching, and I didn't want people to miss the deadline because they're too busy adding last minute additions to costumes. <G>Â 




Registration is free (and so are the waterpark passes!), and the only upfront charge is one night's hotel fee. Sweet deal!




I hope to see a bunch of you at the Waterpark!


~Kelly
